<script>
import axios from 'axios';
export default {
  components: {

  data() {
    return {
      invoice: [],
    };
  },
  created() {
    this.getInvoice();
  },
  methods: {
    async getInvoice() {
      try {
        const inv = await axios.get('getData');
        this.invoice = inv.data;
      } catch (error) {
        console.log(error);
      }
    },
</script>
